body:
{{item:3802}} ----&gt; {{item:3165}} 

As someone who has played the game since Season 2, it is sad that skills such as mana management when playing any AP related character doesn&#039;t exist anymore. This item is also one of the biggest reasons why many Mages will never see any interesting AP item choices because of how inherently strong it is for laning. I don&#039;t know why this item has been allowed to be a staple for so long. It&#039;s probably not as exciting when you can&#039;t watch people spam their abilities, but it&#039;s a little ridiculous that Mages are even allowed to do that in the first place. 

**Idc about LC$. Mages are are supposed to be gated by mana requirements.**
